In the next two blocks,
we will now go into detail

119
00:07:16,417 --> 00:07:18,184
and first talk about energy

120
00:07:19,004 --> 00:07:21,354
and then talk about transportation.

121
00:07:21,354 --> 00:07:24,196
And, here again, we will see
much more concretely

122
00:07:24,776 --> 00:07:26,782
how all these things play out:

123
00:07:26,782 --> 00:07:31,636
the management functions,
the stakeholder functions,

124
00:07:31,636 --> 00:07:33,446
and, of course, the role

125
00:07:33,446 --> 00:07:36,446
of the information 
communication technologies.

126
